1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 10=

3
00:00:11,839 --> 00:00:12,880
Get on your knees.

4
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:25,239
I'll kill you!

5
00:00:27,640 --> 00:00:28,640
(What's happening?)

6
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:31,519
Before I rushed into the fire,

7
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:34,640
I already felt the searing heat
burning my skin.

8
00:00:35,640 --> 00:00:39,759
It must be a shared perception.

9
00:00:41,399 --> 00:00:42,200
(Zechen.)

10
00:00:45,560 --> 00:00:48,799
I told you to keep Qiao Nian
under control.

11
00:00:49,479 --> 00:00:50,719
Now you're divorced.

12
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:53,560
So, how exactly are you going
to control her?

13
00:00:55,119 --> 00:01:00,280
You're the one who made Qiao Wenjun
and me betray her at the meeting.

14
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:02,479
You didn't see this coming either.

15
00:01:02,679 --> 00:01:04,200
That was then.

16
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:05,599
Things are different now.

17
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:10,200
If you can't win Qiao Nian back,

18
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:15,280
I can't promise your brother
will stay alive.

19
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:17,920
(Zechen, wait for me.)

20
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,159
(Keep yourself safe.)

21
00:01:19,439 --> 00:01:20,480
Fine.

22
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,959
I'll do it.

23
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,799
Even so,

24
00:01:28,879 --> 00:01:32,519
you still need to be taught a lesson.

25
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:37,359
Pain makes people remember.

26
00:01:39,239 --> 00:01:42,280
Maybe next time, you won't screw up.

27
00:01:47,439 --> 00:01:48,359
Take that!

28
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:49,439
You little brat!

29
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:51,280
Still won't learn?

30
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,400
I'll beat you senseless!

31
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:53,400
Stop!

32
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:56,799
Move!

33
00:02:04,439 --> 00:02:06,040
Come on. Let's go home.

34
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,199
(Why is she back?)

35
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:13,159
(Did she find out something?)

36
00:02:18,159 --> 00:02:20,280
Nian, he upset you.

37
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,800
I was punishing him for you.

38
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,840
We'll handle our own problems.

39
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,960
Stay out of it.

40
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:32,719
Careful.

41
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,680
(Just you wait.)

42
00:02:41,159 --> 00:02:45,039
(Soon, Qiao Group will be mine.)

43
00:02:51,919 --> 00:02:52,360
Wait here.

44
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,410
I'll get the first aid kit.

45
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,080
Um...

46
00:03:01,759 --> 00:03:03,919
Sit down for a bit.

47
00:03:06,340 --> 00:03:09,100
♪The sky's waiting for the fog to clear♪

48
00:03:09,740 --> 00:03:13,220
♪Like ears waiting for an answer♪

49
00:03:18,439 --> 00:03:20,319
(She put it away.)

50
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:22,479
(So, she must have forgiven me.)

51
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,879
Don't read that.

52
00:03:29,660 --> 00:03:34,879
♪Yet I still look at you at the end♪

53
00:03:34,879 --> 00:03:36,000
Take your shirt off.

54
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:45,840
(Has he been suffering
like this his whole life?)

55
00:03:48,220 --> 00:03:51,100
♪Time tells me to let go♪

56
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,360
Does it hurt?

57
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,919
Did no one teach you

58
00:03:58,199 --> 00:04:00,759
not to touch things
in someone else's house?

59
00:04:02,159 --> 00:04:03,360
This is my home.

60
00:04:03,759 --> 00:04:04,800
I changed the passcode.

61
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:08,280
From now on, knock before coming in.

62
00:04:13,199 --> 00:04:14,000
Then...

63
00:04:15,159 --> 00:04:18,519
does that mean I can visit here anytime?

64
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,519
Ah!

65
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:24,639
Did I hurt you?

66
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,079
It's fine.

67
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:29,480
I'm used to it.

68
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,160
I just...

69
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,120
dragged you into this.

70
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,519
I'm fine.

71
00:04:39,519 --> 00:04:40,319
But...

72
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:44,120
you've been carrying
this pain all along.

73
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:46,560
From now on,

74
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:50,800
don't rush over
just because you feel what I feel.

75
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:52,000
Got it?

76
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,959
Is this because of your brother?

77
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:01,600
You never told me any of this.

78
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:04,720
Why?

79
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,279
I...

80
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:11,439
I didn't want you to see at my worst.

81
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,399
I'm sorry.

82
00:05:19,199 --> 00:05:20,959
I didn't mean to keep it from you.

83
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:31,399
(How much have you suffered for me?)

84
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,279
Will you...

85
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,759
stay with me?

86
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,439
If you behave.

87
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:49,800
Right.

88
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,560
There's something else.

89
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:54,639
When I was at your dad's place,

90
00:05:54,639 --> 00:05:56,800
I heard my mom's dolphin bracelet.

91
00:05:58,839 --> 00:06:00,759
At first, I thought I'd imagined it.

92
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:04,279
But it felt way too real.

93
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:08,480
I checked my mom's connections before.

94
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:11,360
It turns out she and Jiang Xiao
were college classmates.

95
00:06:13,319 --> 00:06:14,120
But

96
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:19,639
your mom's classmates said
they barely interacted.

97
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:21,600
That's the strange part.

98
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,360
It's okay.

99
00:06:26,399 --> 00:06:27,560
I'll find out what happened.

100
00:06:29,079 --> 00:06:29,879
Thanks.

101
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,639
Thank you.

102
00:06:43,639 --> 00:06:45,439
Ah!

103
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:47,639
Why is it you again?

104
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,079
You just won't go away.

105
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:51,720
What are you doing here?

106
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,560
Why should I tell you?

107
00:06:54,279 --> 00:06:56,720
Trust me, you don't want to go up there.

108
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,519
Jiang Zechen is inside.

109
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:02,319
Why should I listen to you?

110
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:05,600
Oh, come on.

111
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,399
Wait.

112
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:08,079
Look.

113
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,279
No rush.

114
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,160
Go in later.

115
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,879
Those two look suspicious.

116
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:16,040
They're definitely up to something.

117
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:17,879
Then we have to tell Qiao Nian.

118
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,879
I already called Zechen.

119
00:07:33,759 --> 00:07:35,800
Qiao Nian, don't be scared.

120
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:47,759
Follow my lead.

121
00:08:18,279 --> 00:08:19,959
Qiao Nian, are you okay?

122
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:29,040
Mr. and Mrs. Smith, huh?

123
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,279
Talk.

124
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,879
Who sent you?

125
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:43,960
It was...

126
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:47,799
President Qiao. She wanted Qiao Nian
brought to her.

127
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,399
I knew it.

128
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,879
And if we refuse?

129
00:08:51,879 --> 00:08:52,399
Then I'll...

130
00:08:59,039 --> 00:09:00,159
Thanks

131
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:02,519
for calling us in advance.

132
00:09:02,519 --> 00:09:04,320
I don't even know your name yet.

133
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:05,559
Thanks.

134
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:06,080
Ahem.

135
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:09,279
Mr. Jiang, that's your cue
to introduce me.

136
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,000
Fine.

137
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:14,799
This is Wen Li,
heiress of the Wen family.

138
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:16,879
Also, a blogger
with eight million followers.

139
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,200
I'm a hacker, okay?

140
00:09:20,759 --> 00:09:22,279
Nice to meet you, Wen Li.

141
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,399
Alright.

142
00:09:26,879 --> 00:09:30,320
Qiao Wenjun didn't send them here
for nothing.

143
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:34,200
The factory!

144
00:09:34,639 --> 00:09:36,639
She sent them to buy herself time.

145
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:38,320
I have to go now.

146
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,039
I'm coming with you.

147
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:39,720
Me too.

148
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:49,399
Wait. What's it to you?

149
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:52,000
With me around,
Qiao Wenjun won't touch Qiao Nian.

150
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:08,050
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

151
00:10:08,330 --> 00:10:15,930
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

152
00:10:15,980 --> 00:10:19,770
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

153
00:10:20,290 --> 00:10:23,570
♪Where this ends♪

154
00:10:23,570 --> 00:10:30,850
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

155
00:10:30,850 --> 00:10:35,180
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

156
00:10:35,220 --> 00:10:38,300
♪Love turns into pain♪

157
00:10:38,370 --> 00:10:42,490
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

158
00:10:42,650 --> 00:10:46,130
♪Yet I still want you close♪

159
00:10:46,130 --> 00:10:50,300
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

160
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:53,610
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

161
00:10:53,610 --> 00:10:58,180
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

162
00:10:58,180 --> 00:11:04,490
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

163
